nanoc-sprockets (1.0.5) stable;

  * add support for both Nanoc 3.x and Nanoc 4.x
  * provide better error output
  * fix missing documentation on debug mode

nanoc-sprockets (1.0.4) stable;

  * add support for Sprockets ~> 3.2, >= 3.0.0
  * add debug mode for verbose output

nanoc-sprockets (1.0.3) stable;

  * add support for Sprockets 3.x.beta.8
  * add CHANGELOG

nanoc-sprockets (1.0.3) stable;

  * add support for digest paths
  * fix bug in default Sprockets env definition
  
nanoc-sprockets (1.0.0) stable;

  * bring support to sprockets 3.x.beta to nanoc
